{"id":489073,"date":[{"year":1968,"month":3,"day":30}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"215","ytitle":"","mtitle":"纺织机旁谱新歌","ftitle":"","authors":["汪婉华","殷银珠","周美华发"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“公”字明灯亮心头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第八丝织厂　汪婉华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作捧在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“公”字明灯亮心头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银梭飞起万匹绸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海铺锦绣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心织出向阳篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国棉十九厂　殷银珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫看机弄二尺宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是革命跑道线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席指引我巡回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心织出向阳篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席宝书擎在手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国棉九厂　周美华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席宝书擎在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈开风浪大步走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸有朝阳飞银梭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织出红旗飘全球!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银梭飞线立新功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红纺织机械厂　龚咏燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新指示象明灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮布机照红心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银梭飞线立新功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大红旗下布潮涌!"}]}